title: 1 bed room with washer/dryer, top floor
posting_body: A smile will be on your face when you come in to see your new home here at Hunters Glen!
Friendly on-site management and maintenance teams are here for you!
Our 1 bedroom apartments have a washer/dryer in the unit as well as reserved covered parking!
We are just a few minutes away from JBLM and Lakewood Town Center shopping, close to everything you need.
Call today for more details and to schedule a visit to select your new home.
Prices, availability and terms are subject to change without notice and subject to approval of application.
